uti, S., (1971) Synopsis of Digenetic Trematodes of Vertebrates, 1. , Keigaku Publishing Co., Tokyo","Pech, D.; Laboratorio de Parasitología, Departamento de Recursos del Mar, Cinvestav, Carretera antigua a Progreso km 6, Apdo. Postal 73 - Cordemex, 97310 Mérida, Yucatán, Mexico; email: danielpech@uacam.mx",,,,,,,,00207519,,IJPYB,20178804,"English","Int. J. Parasitol.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-77953019787
